tweet: Forex Robot World Cup is a first competition of forex trading robots based on live money performance. Sponsored by FXCM and Boston Tech.
For the first time ever, non-commercial robot developers from all over the world will have a chance to compete in the automated championship
December 1 2009 Live trading phase has begun!!
The FRWC is proud to announce that 329 EAs were submitted throughout the first phase of the competition.
From the EAs submitted, 24 met the high standards of the FRWC rules and qualified for the live trading phase.
